WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 15=

00:00:05.220 --> 00:00:07.019
Who else was it supposed to be,

00:00:07.020 --> 00:00:08.700
Zhu Lingtai?

00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:10.620
Your Highness.

00:00:10.820 --> 00:00:13.759
Many years ago, the Imperial Preceptor
of the Imperial Observatory once foretold

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:15.619
that I was a lone star of misfortune,

00:00:15.620 --> 00:00:17.200
doomed to bring harm
to my family and lord.

00:00:17.740 --> 00:00:19.180
Could it be

00:00:19.260 --> 00:00:21.140
that Zhu Lingtai now believes

00:00:21.660 --> 00:00:24.420
the Crown Prince is a monster too?

00:00:25.620 --> 00:00:27.219
I would never dare, Your Highness.

00:00:27.220 --> 00:00:28.980
Your Majesty, please see clearly.

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:31.660
Just now,
you sounded completely certain.

00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:33.660
Why change your tune all of a sudden?

00:00:34.420 --> 00:00:36.619
Could it be the one instructing you

00:00:36.620 --> 00:00:38.340
wasn't fate,

00:00:38.700 --> 00:00:39.820
but a person?

00:00:40.420 --> 00:00:42.860
Prince Jing, what are you saying?

00:00:43.420 --> 00:00:44.299
Zhu Lingtai

00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:46.180
is only doing his duty.

00:00:47.060 --> 00:00:48.459
Since ancient times,

00:00:48.460 --> 00:00:50.380
fortune and disaster
have always gone hand in hand.

00:00:50.620 --> 00:00:52.300
A slight mistake

00:00:52.340 --> 00:00:53.979
is understandable.

00:00:53.980 --> 00:00:55.220
Right?

00:01:00.420 --> 00:01:01.139
Yes.

00:01:01.140 --> 00:01:02.259
Her Highness is right.

00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:04.739
I carefully observed
the stars again just now.

00:01:04.740 --> 00:01:06.380
I truly made a mistake.

00:01:06.460 --> 00:01:08.459
This isn't an evil star clashing
with the Purple Star.

00:01:08.460 --> 00:01:09.420
Instead...

00:01:09.860 --> 00:01:11.539
Instead, it's an auspicious omen.

00:01:11.540 --> 00:01:12.380
Your Majesty.

00:01:13.140 --> 00:01:15.619
Yes. Today is Your Majesty's birthday.

00:01:15.620 --> 00:01:17.659
A great blessing is bound to appear.

00:01:17.660 --> 00:01:19.220
I observed the stars,

00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:20.459
and this blessing...

00:01:20.460 --> 00:01:23.180
This blessing
should have already arrived.

00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:30.620
Hmm.

00:01:31.420 --> 00:01:32.659
Your Majesty, the blessing!

00:01:32.660 --> 00:01:35.460
Look, it really is a blessing!

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:37.099
So annoying!

00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:40.419
What's with all this blessing nonsense?
They insistedon smearing this stuff on me.

00:01:40.420 --> 00:01:42.940
What even is this thing?
It's so uncomfortable stuck on me.

00:01:43.420 --> 00:01:44.739
Hahaha!

00:01:44.740 --> 00:01:45.419
What a fine deer.

00:01:45.420 --> 00:01:46.420
What a fine deer.

00:01:47.060 --> 00:01:48.620
(Good thing I came prepared.)

00:01:48.740 --> 00:01:52.180
(I may not be able to harm that little jinx,
at least it'll help my son save face.)

00:01:54.100 --> 00:01:54.859
Yes,

00:01:54.860 --> 00:01:55.859
just like that.

00:01:55.860 --> 00:01:56.859
Slow down.

00:01:56.860 --> 00:01:58.059
Be graceful.

00:01:58.060 --> 00:01:59.499
Once you've walked a few more steps,

00:01:59.500 --> 00:02:02.259
find the person carrying
the scent and lick them once.

00:02:02.260 --> 00:02:03.940
Then I'll get something tasty to eat.

00:02:07.620 --> 00:02:08.179
Father.

00:02:08.180 --> 00:02:09.620
That's a fake deer.

00:02:10.300 --> 00:02:11.659
Watch closely.

00:02:11.660 --> 00:02:13.740
I'll perform a trick for Grandfather.

00:02:16.780 --> 00:02:17.459
Grandfather.

00:02:17.460 --> 00:02:18.859
The divine deer has arrived.

00:02:18.860 --> 00:02:21.299
We need some music for it.

00:02:21.300 --> 00:02:22.259
Hey.

00:02:22.260 --> 00:02:23.420
There's such a thing?

00:02:33.300 --> 00:02:35.899
- Don't you think this sounds awful?
- You simply don't appreciate it.

00:02:35.900 --> 00:02:36.620
You...

00:02:37.100 --> 00:02:37.899
That sound...

00:02:37.900 --> 00:02:39.220
That sound is pretty nice.

00:02:39.260 --> 00:02:39.939
Wait.

00:02:39.940 --> 00:02:42.940
Why can I understand this sound?
Young Mistress of the Mystic Crow Clan?

00:02:43.300 --> 00:02:44.019
(Don't come over.)

00:02:44.020 --> 00:02:45.259
(Dance while answering me.)

00:02:45.260 --> 00:02:47.480
(My grandfather likes it.
I want to ask you something.)

00:02:47.480 --> 00:02:49.440
(How much did they give you
to put on this act?)

00:02:49.440 --> 00:02:50.619
Just a basket of apples.

00:02:50.620 --> 00:02:51.739
They're so stingy.

00:02:51.740 --> 00:02:53.219
Not only did they paint me white,

00:02:53.220 --> 00:02:56.139
they also told me to find someone
wearing perfume and lick them.

00:02:56.140 --> 00:02:58.219
Look at that person.

00:02:58.220 --> 00:02:59.499
He looks like a horse.

00:02:59.500 --> 00:03:01.179
We deer don't like that.

00:03:01.180 --> 00:03:02.059
(I see.)

00:03:02.060 --> 00:03:04.580
(I'll give you three times as much.
Just cooperate with me.)

00:03:04.940 --> 00:03:06.980
Deal.

00:03:07.980 --> 00:03:09.700
Zhu Lingtai.

00:03:11.220 --> 00:03:12.460
Your Majesty, please see clearly.

00:03:13.100 --> 00:03:15.819
This auspicious beast
is a divine creature sent from heaven.

00:03:15.820 --> 00:03:19.099
It will naturally approach
those blessed with great fortune.

00:03:19.100 --> 00:03:22.419
It merely danced
along with the Little Princess.

00:03:22.420 --> 00:03:25.740
Their connection
simply isn't deep enough.

00:03:28.540 --> 00:03:29.619
Your Majesty, look.

00:03:29.620 --> 00:03:32.060
The divine deer chose the Crown Prince!

00:03:51.900 --> 00:03:54.740
Hahahaha!

00:03:54.780 --> 00:03:55.739
You beast!

00:03:55.740 --> 00:03:57.299
Drag this beast out of here!

00:03:57.300 --> 00:03:58.119
My son!

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:59.580
My son!

00:03:59.820 --> 00:04:02.580
My son!

00:04:02.660 --> 00:04:04.619
The white paint all over me feels awful.

00:04:04.620 --> 00:04:06.020
I need to shake it off.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:21.039
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:24.879
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:04:24.880 --> 00:04:28.399
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:31.360
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:35.879
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:39.640
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:43.039
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:47.080
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:56.359
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:04:56.360 --> 00:04:59.999
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:03.719
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:07.359
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:11.039
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:11.040 --> 00:05:12.959
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:12.960 --> 00:05:19.160
♪Good fortune♪